    "However, at the time of the study, this parameter was not working as intended and cut longer reappraisals off mid-sentence instead of making a reappraisal of that length.",
    "Importantly, when processing these reappraisals we made sure to remove aspects like spelling mistakes and use of capital letters to make sure that these errors were not drivers of any different discovered between human and GPT-4.",
    "Given that we were aiming for 10 GPT reappraisals per vignette, we made two API calls for each vignette.",
    "Each API request hence included a copy of the reappraisal training and a reappraisal request.",
    "We kept all parameters at default during the requests."
